{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020-04-27-09-02-node-current-directory/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ohmybuck"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"396b2af3-784f-5c19-9913-79d54d53853b","excerpt":"Working with the following directory structure Running the hypothetical script  will produce the following","html":"<p>Working with the following directory structure</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">.</span>\n├── package.json\n├── scripts\n│   └── new-post\n│       ├── index.js\n│       └── post.md.tpl\n└── static\n    ├── CNAME\n    ├── favicon.ico\n    └── robots.txt</code></pre></div>\n<p>Running the hypothetical script <code class=\"language-text\">node scripts/new-post/index.js</code> will produce the following</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">process<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">cwd</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// .</span>\n\n__dirname\n<span class=\"token comment\">// scripts/new-post</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Node Current Directory","date":"April 27, 2020","description":"Node Current Directory"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020-04-27-09-02-node-current-directory/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-04-15-slack-notifications-circle-ci/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Slack Notifications from Circle CI","draft":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020-04-27-09-07-tree-and-git-projects/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tree And Git Projects","draft":null}}}}}